message:
Running command: cd /workspace/SheepVibes && git commit --amend -m "fix: address code review feedback for PR #81

- Enhance backend PUT endpoint to return full feed data including items
- Update frontend to update single widget instead of reloading entire tab
- Clean up redundant CSS for delete button
- Change backend port to 5001 to avoid conflicts
- Improve error handling in backend PUT endpoint

Co-authored-by: openhands <openhands@all-hands.dev>"
